&lt;h2 id=&#34;tech-is-not-neutral&#34;&gt;Tech is not neutral&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;canary-in-a-coal-mine-how-tech-provides-platforms-for-hate&#34;&gt;Canary in a Coal Mine: How Tech Provides Platforms for Hate&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By Tatiana Mac on A List Apart&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;‚ÄúWe, by way of our platforms, give agency and credence to these acts of violence, then pilfer profits from them. Tech is a money-making accomplice to these hate crimes.‚Äù&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Article: &lt;a href=&#34;https://alistapart.com/article/canary-in-a-coal-mine-how-tech-provides-platforms-for-hate&#34;&gt;Canary in a Coal Mine: How Tech Provides Platforms for Hate&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;trading-privacy-for-survival-is-another-tax-on-the-poor&#34;&gt;Trading privacy for survival is another tax on the poor&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By Ciara Byrne on Fast Company&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
