&lt;p&gt;By Gary Younge on The Guardian&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;‚ÄúRacism is not about politeness ‚Äì it‚Äôs about power. What is truly worrying about these blunders is that they have let the mask slip to reveal a political class that, at best, does not understand the racial dynamics of the country in which it operates and, at worst, is deeply hostile to them.‚Äù&lt;/p&gt;
