      src=&#39;panel.jpg&#39; alt=&#39;Matt Alagiah, me, Alex Macleod, Zander Brade and Deborah Goschalk sitting on stools on a stage, I‚Äôm waving my hand while speaking and everyone else is listening to me.&#39;
