&lt;p&gt;Did you read it? Did it help you make more accessible websites? If you didn‚Äôt read it yet (or even want to read it again‚Ä¶!) you can always listen to &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.audible.com/pd/B07G24HLXS&#34;&gt;the audiobook on Audible&lt;/a&gt;. The whole book takes less than an afternoon‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;

