  &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://laurakalbag.com/one-year-bookiversary/&#34;&gt;Read the original post, ‚ÄòOne Year Bookiversary‚Äô&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This post is a follow-up to &lt;a href=&#34;https://laurakalbag.com/whats-wrong-with-twitter&#34;&gt;What‚Äôs wrong with Twitter?&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://framablog.org/2018/09/17/bye-bye-twitter-hello-masto/&#34;&gt;You can read this post en fran√ßais on the Framasoft blog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://joinmastodon.org&#34;&gt;Mastodon&lt;/a&gt; started out as a microblogging platform similar to Twitter, but has evolved with more features that show an ethical, progressive and inclusive focus. Instead of tweets, your posts on Mastodon are called toots.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jump to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#why-use-mastodon-and-not-another-new-social-network&#34;&gt;Why use Mastodon and not another new social network?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#how-to-use-mastodon&#34;&gt;How to use Mastodon&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#my-instance-of-one&#34;&gt;My instance-of-one&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#how-to-set-up-an-instance-of-one&#34;&gt;How to set up an instance-of-one&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#but-but-but&#34;&gt;But but but&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#join-me-there&#34;&gt;Join me there!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;



