&lt;p&gt;It‚Äôs thanks to the hard work of my brother, Sam Kalbag, who single-handedly edited, engineered and produced the audiobook, helped me do the recording properly, and gave me the benefit of his extensive knowledge of audiobooks. And also Katel LeD√ª, A Book Apart‚Äôs CEO and all-round publishing legend, who navigated the Audible process for us all.&lt;/p&gt;

