&lt;p&gt;It‚Äôs been a few years since I wrote something for &lt;a href=&#34;http://24ways.org&#34;&gt;24ways&lt;/a&gt;, but this year I‚Äôm back, &lt;a href=&#34;https://24ways.org/2017/accessibility-through-semantic-html/&#34;&gt;making the case for semantic HTML&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;


    &lt;a
      href=&#39;https://24ways.org/2017/accessibility-through-semantic-html/&#39;
    &gt;

    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;1920&#39; height=&#39;1028&#39;
