&lt;p&gt;Nearly two years ago, my mother died. We didn‚Äôt want any of our friends and family finding out from a poorly thought-out tweet or Facebook post‚Ä¶ so we didn‚Äôt post anything on social media. We rang people to let them know. And then Facebook suggested I might be interested in‚Ä¶ Goodwill Family Funeral Directors.&lt;/p&gt;



