    /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let‚Äôs have a closer look at these sites‚Ä¶ there are a few that are familiar to developers‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Google Analytics&lt;/strong&gt;, we know that‚Äôs analytics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Twitter and Facebook&lt;/strong&gt;, possibly some kind of sharing buttons (but also possibly not)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But that leaves 21 more mysterious scripts‚Ä¶ Let‚Äôs have a close look at one of those sites‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;



