    /&gt;
      &lt;/a&gt;


&lt;p&gt;As we become more aware of the problems, the people behind the trackers are getting defensive. Massive German publisher &lt;a href=&#34;https://better.fyi/spotlight&#34;&gt;Axel Springer says their ‚Äúcore business is delivering ads to its visitors. Journalistic content is just a vehicle to get readers to view the ads‚Äù&lt;/a&gt;. According to Lindsay Rowntree, who writes for a marketing and advertising blog‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;‚ÄúThe web, as it is today, exists because of an implicit understanding that ads pay for the content consumers love and, therefore, need to be seen.‚Äù&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;‚Äî&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.exchangewire.com/blog/2016/05/18/why-threes-partnership-with-%20shine-makes-publishers-more-vulnerable-than-ever/&#34;&gt;Lindsay Rowntree, Why Three‚Äôs Partnership with Shine‚Ä¶, May 2016&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Again. No. This is just not true. Ads are the most common business model, but not the only one. Do you want to get all your news from people who just want your eyeballs? And remember, ads are still not the problem. Trackers are the problem.&lt;/p&gt;



    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;1280&#39; height=&#39;720&#39;
      sizes=&#39;(min-width: 1380px) 750px, (min-width: 820px) 719px, (min-width: 740px) calc(-33.33vw &amp;#43; 875px), (min-width: 340px) calc(92.63vw - 39px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#39;
      srcset=&#39;https://laurakalbag.com/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/424_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_104512_300x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 300w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/424_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_104512_500x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 500w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/424_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_104512_800x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 800w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/424_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_104512_1200x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 1200w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/424.jpg 1280w&#39;
      src=&#39;424.jpg&#39; alt=&#39;Corporations need to stop treating us like we‚Äôre greedy lab rats&#39;
    /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Corporations need to stop treating us like we‚Äôre greedy lab rats, making outrageous demands just by asking¬†‚Äúplease don‚Äôt experiment on us.‚Äù&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We must question and challenge these unethical practices. And we need to learn to see past the &lt;abbr title=&#34;Public Relations&#34;&gt;PR&lt;/abbr&gt;. We certainly shouldn‚Äôt engage in this PR ourselves. We need to make real things that have meaning, rather than the illusion of having meaning. Don‚Äôt be the person shaving a few kilobytes off an image file when someone else is adding 5MB of trackers.&lt;/p&gt;



    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;1280&#39; height=&#39;720&#39;
      sizes=&#39;(min-width: 1380px) 750px, (min-width: 820px) 719px, (min-width: 740px) calc(-33.33vw &amp;#43; 875px), (min-width: 340px) calc(92.63vw - 39px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#39;
      srcset=&#39;https://laurakalbag.com/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/428_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_53645_300x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 300w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/428_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_53645_500x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 500w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/428_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_53645_800x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 800w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/428_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_53645_1200x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 1200w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/428.jpg 1280w&#39;
      src=&#39;428.jpg&#39; alt=&#39;Save our jobs&#39;
    /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should also be selfish. Building ethical alternatives to centralised technologies will save our jobs. &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/06/business/facebook-bends-the-rules-of-audience-engagement-to-its-advantage.html&#34;&gt;The average Facebook user spends 50 minutes on Facebook a day&lt;/a&gt;. Facebook‚Äôs functionality has replaced status updates, photo sharing, company sites, news, and chat, to name just a few.&lt;/p&gt;



    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;1280&#39; height=&#39;720&#39;
      sizes=&#39;(min-width: 1380px) 750px, (min-width: 820px) 719px, (min-width: 740px) calc(-33.33vw &amp;#43; 875px), (min-width: 340px) calc(92.63vw - 39px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#39;
      srcset=&#39;https://laurakalbag.com/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/435_hue9fa5f2c6d9d7e4bc32541af0fb06880_54338_300x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 300w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/435_hue9fa5f2c6d9d7e4bc32541af0fb06880_54338_500x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 500w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/435_hue9fa5f2c6d9d7e4bc32541af0fb06880_54338_800x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 800w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/435_hue9fa5f2c6d9d7e4bc32541af0fb06880_54338_1200x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 1200w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/435.jpg 1280w&#39;
      src=&#39;435.jpg&#39; alt=&#39;Status updates, Instagram, Facebook Messenger, Facebook Pages&#39;
    /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When it comes to our business use, what Facebook hasn‚Äôt got covered, Google has a product for you. If we want jobs that aren‚Äôt at Facebook or Google,¬†we‚Äôre going to need to make sure the rest of the web actually exists.&lt;/p&gt;



    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;1280&#39; height=&#39;720&#39;
      sizes=&#39;(min-width: 1380px) 750px, (min-width: 820px) 719px, (min-width: 740px) calc(-33.33vw &amp;#43; 875px), (min-width: 340px) calc(92.63vw - 39px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#39;
      srcset=&#39;https://laurakalbag.com/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/436_huceeae38135e9be045a6d922aa2389849_213599_300x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 300w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/436_huceeae38135e9be045a6d922aa2389849_213599_500x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 500w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/436_huceeae38135e9be045a6d922aa2389849_213599_800x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 800w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/436_huceeae38135e9be045a6d922aa2389849_213599_1200x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 1200w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/436.jpg 1280w&#39;
      src=&#39;436.jpg&#39; alt=&#39;All the Google products&#39;
    /&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;build-and-support-alternatives&#34;&gt;Build and support alternatives&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We need to build alternatives, giving ourselves the choice to choose a different way, as both the consumers and the builders of the web. And when we find alternatives, we must support them.&lt;/p&gt;



    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;1280&#39; height=&#39;720&#39;
      sizes=&#39;(min-width: 1380px) 750px, (min-width: 820px) 719px, (min-width: 740px) calc(-33.33vw &amp;#43; 875px), (min-width: 340px) calc(92.63vw - 39px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#39;
      srcset=&#39;https://laurakalbag.com/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/438_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_69250_300x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 300w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/438_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_69250_500x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 500w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/438_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_69250_800x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 800w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/438_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_69250_1200x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 1200w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/438.jpg 1280w&#39;
      src=&#39;438.jpg&#39; alt=&#39;Build and support alternatives&#39;
    /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When you‚Äôre looking for replacements for Facebook and Google products, don‚Äôt just look for another behemoth. You can‚Äôt replace Google in its entirety, but you can use individual products/services to replace different parts of its functionality. Perhaps DuckDuckGo for search, OpenStreetMap for maps, WordPress for blogging, Fastmail for email. The benefit of using individual products is that no one organisation has all your information.&lt;/p&gt;



    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;1280&#39; height=&#39;720&#39;
      sizes=&#39;(min-width: 1380px) 750px, (min-width: 820px) 719px, (min-width: 740px) calc(-33.33vw &amp;#43; 875px), (min-width: 340px) calc(92.63vw - 39px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#39;
      srcset=&#39;https://laurakalbag.com/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/441_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_90845_300x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 300w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/441_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_90845_500x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 500w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/441_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_90845_800x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 800w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/441_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_90845_1200x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 1200w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/441.jpg 1280w&#39;
      src=&#39;441.jpg&#39; alt=&#39;Look for traditional business models&#39;
    /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It‚Äôs also worth looking for organisations that have traditional business models. Business models where you pay for a product or service in small one-off or recurring fees. With larger organisations, that‚Äôs no guarantee that they won‚Äôt track you, but small-to-medium businesses are less likely to take your money and track you too.&lt;/p&gt;



    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;1280&#39; height=&#39;720&#39;
      sizes=&#39;(min-width: 1380px) 750px, (min-width: 820px) 719px, (min-width: 740px) calc(-33.33vw &amp;#43; 875px), (min-width: 340px) calc(92.63vw - 39px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#39;
      srcset=&#39;https://laurakalbag.com/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/442_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_65567_300x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 300w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/442_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_65567_500x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 500w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/442_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_65567_800x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 800w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/442_hu6642974bf16ed882bf8486f57a8a55c3_65567_1200x0_resize_q80_mitchellnetravali.jpg 1200w,/digital-assistants-facebook-quizzes-and-fake-news-you-wont-believe-what-happens-next/442.jpg 1280w&#39;
      src=&#39;442.jpg&#39; alt=&#39;Call out bad behaviour&#39;
    /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It‚Äôs also vitally important that we call out bad behaviour and make tracking socially unacceptable. Call out businesses you see tracking you, &lt;em&gt;especially&lt;/em&gt; if you also pay them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;work-for-more-ethical-companies&#34;&gt;Work for more ethical companies&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can‚Äôt all just quit our jobs to go work somewhere more ethical, but maybe next time you‚Äôre looking for work, do your research on their business models. Help make a difference by putting your valuable knowledge and skills into building the alternatives, and help us build these bridges from the mainstream technology to the future we want to see.&lt;/p&gt;



    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;1280&#39; height=&#39;720&#39;
      sizes=&#39;(min-width: 1380px) 750px, (min-width: 820px) 719px, (min-width: 740px) calc(-33.33vw &amp;#43; 875px), (min-width: 340px) calc(92.63vw - 39px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#39;
