&lt;p&gt;My site is looking a little different, I‚Äôm now using the lovely &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.indiantypefoundry.com/fonts/recia&#34;&gt;Recia&lt;/a&gt; for the type. &lt;a href=&#34;http://blog.fontdeck.com/post/133794978966/why-fontdeck-is-retiring&#34;&gt;Fontdeck recently retired&lt;/a&gt;, and while they gave &lt;em&gt;loads&lt;/em&gt; of notice about the service stopping, I still didn‚Äôt update my fonts in time. This left¬†my site looking a little sad and Helvetica-y.&lt;/p&gt;

