&lt;p&gt;I have a redesign in the works. But¬†I‚Äôve no idea¬†when it‚Äôll be finished.¬†It requires a major reworking in the focus of the site itself. Since I‚Äôve been full time with &lt;a href=&#34;https://ind.ie&#34;&gt;Ind.ie&lt;/a&gt;, the portfolio element of the site is a bit redundant. Although it‚Äôs nice to have a history of work, and I‚Äôd really like to use it for case studies of the design work for Ind.ie and &lt;a href=&#34;https://better.fyi&#34;&gt;Better&lt;/a&gt;. Most of my writing has also appeared on Ind.ie, or on other sites,¬†but needs to be linked to from here. It‚Äôs also time I got my head around all the WordPress theming changes from the last couple of years.&lt;/p&gt;

