&lt;p&gt;It‚Äôs not even been a week since 51.9% UK citizens voted to leave the EU, and it‚Äôs already a mess for any business operating from, or with, British Pounds. I‚Äôve spent today working through our finances to see how best for us to proceed in terms of currencies and bank accounts. Despite living in Sweden, we‚Äôre still tied to the UK, not least because I‚Äôm a British citizen‚Ä¶ * shakes fist at the idiots who voted to Leave *&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Other than the Brexit woes, we‚Äôve been working hard on keeping Better up-to-date and fixing any teething problems we‚Äôve had with the trackers list. Since launch we‚Äôve updated Better (the app) twice, and updated the content (the tracker list) seven times. We‚Äôve had loads of great reviews on the App Store, and reading these are encouraging, motivational, and the best way to start our days! :smile:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôre now working on the best trackers to target next, and ways to keep improving Better. As well as how to continue raising awareness alongside promoting sales to help keep us sustainable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Oh, and I nearly forgot the‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;
