&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://laurakalbag.com/diary-29th-june-2016/&#34;&gt;Read the original post, ‚ÄòDiary, 29th June 2016‚Äô&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Time rolls by and it‚Äôs about time I did another diary entry. I‚Äôm going to try to get Aral and me to write more frequently now what we‚Äôre working on (&lt;a href=&#34;https://better.fyi&#34;&gt;Better&lt;/a&gt;) is out in the open. (No more talk of the hush-hush project! ;-)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Since the launch of Better, we‚Äôve been keeping development going, whilst making improvements to the Better app and Better.fyi, as well as responding to emails, tweets, feedback and questions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As well as keeping the financial and admin side ticking over, recently my biggest tasks have been getting the &lt;a href=&#34;https://better.fyi/reviews/&#34;&gt;Reviews on to Better.fyi&lt;/a&gt;, so people can see all the great stuff that has been said about Better before they buy. This is, so far, the best job ever. You don‚Äôt know how encouraging and exhilarating it is to read through brand new 5* reviews on a daily basis. I‚Äôve danced in the office, and Aral and I have high-fived our hands raw. Thank you to those of you who have left such wonderful reviews, it has not only given us encouragement, but also let other people on the App Store know what Better is about.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We also added a &lt;a href=&#34;https://better.fyi/support/&#34;&gt;Support page&lt;/a&gt; to Better.fyi to answer some of the most common questions. This was something that would‚Äôve been harder to do before the launch as we weren‚Äôt entirely sure what would come up. These questions have also shaped the rest of our copy in the app and on Better.fyi.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hopefully I‚Äôll be back to give you another update soon!&lt;/p&gt;
