&lt;p&gt;Always busy here! Aral and I have been doing a good job of getting out to events in our new home city of Malm√∂. Last week we went to see¬†&lt;a href=&#34;https://forum.ind.ie/t/a-good-american-doc-lounge-screening-in-malmo/1135&#34;&gt;A Good American at DocLounge&lt;/a&gt;, and this week we‚Äôve been to a few events right here in¬†[Media Evolution City](&lt;a href=&#34;http://mediaevolutioncity.se/%22&#34;&gt;http://mediaevolutioncity.se/&amp;quot;&lt;/a&gt; rel=&amp;ldquo;nofollow). We‚Äôre really lucky to have an amazing venue that hosts so many events around us.&lt;/p&gt;
