&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;3rd July: NEW BOOKS ADDED!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://aralbalkan.com/notes/so-long-and-thanks-for-all-the-fish/&#34;&gt;We‚Äôre moving&lt;/a&gt;. And because we‚Äôre moving abroad, we‚Äôre &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.gumtree.com/sellerads/1119077228&#34;&gt;getting rid of all of our stuff&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#books&#34;&gt;Just take me to the books already&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://aralbalkan.com/notes/so-long-and-thanks-for-all-the-fish/&#34;&gt;Aral&lt;/a&gt; and I have a lot of books between us. We‚Äôre sad to lose them. Many have been gifts from friends, written by people we know, and helped us do¬†what we do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Selling books one by one is a time-consuming (and not cost-effective) exercise. Inspired by my friend Al Power coming over and asking ‚Äúwhich books do you have on Typography?‚Äù I thought they‚Äôd be worth selling as bundles. All these books are worth way more than we‚Äôre selling them for, but we‚Äôre in a rush and want them to go to good homes. I‚Äôve not done any particularly complicated pricing. Small books are ¬£8¬†per bundle. Four small books: ¬£10. Two small books:¬†¬£5. Big books are ¬£12 per bundle. Big book bundles with two books are ¬£10. They‚Äôre all in good condition, most nearly-new. A few come with bonus margin notes‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There‚Äôs more (lots of bigger books) coming! If people show interest in this, we‚Äôve got more on typography, art, programming languages and more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;postage-options&#34;&gt;Postage options&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The problem with books is that they cost a fortune to post. So I‚Äôve bundled them all under 2kg so we can keep the post cheap. (Oddly, 2kg costs more to post than 2 x 1kg.) They fall into two categories: below 1kg, and above 1kg. (Listed alongside the bundles)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want them 2nd class to save the pennies, that‚Äôs cool too.&lt;/p&gt;
