      &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;First photo on manual&lt;/strong&gt;. Fallen at the first hurdle, I turned my settings on to manual and fiddled with the shutter speed and aperture but couldn‚Äôt seem to get any exposure at all.&lt;/p&gt;

