&lt;p&gt;Another fab and in-depth article from Craig Grannell on Digital Arts, this time on¬†&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.digitalartsonline.co.uk/features/interactive-design/web-fonts-what-designers-need-to-know-in-2015/&#34;&gt;Web fonts: what designers need to know in 2015&lt;/a&gt;. Craig asked a load of smart designers (and me) about web fonts, web font services, and how to choose web fonts.&lt;/p&gt;


