@Damian thanks :)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I find there‚Äôs benefits in both working freelance and in a team. There‚Äôs less disruption during the working day if you‚Äôre working alone. But when you work in a team you can make more progress coming up with ideas, learning from each other, and bouncing thoughts and problems around.
