&lt;p&gt;After a few months of being pretty quiet, and working towards our crowdfunding campaign, we‚Äôre finally able to reveal &lt;a href=&#34;https://ind.ie/&#34;&gt;some big stuff about ind.ie&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôre not just designing a phone. A crowdfunding campaign for a phone that you‚Äôll get in two years is not a risk worth taking. We need to build a network and ecosystem around that phone. We need a fantastic and mature platform that the phone to give the phone the ultimate experience on its release. So that‚Äôs what we‚Äôre building. It‚Äôs not just a phone. It‚Äôs not just hardware, software and cloud services. We‚Äôre going post-cloud and creating hardware, software, a peer-to-peer network and all of this will be part of the ind.ie ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
