&lt;p&gt;Andy Clarke is on holiday for three weeks and has handed over the &lt;a href=&#34;http://unfinished.bz/&#34;&gt;Unfinished Business&lt;/a&gt; reins to &lt;a href=&#34;http://insurancebyjack.co.uk/&#34;&gt;Ashley Baxter&lt;/a&gt; and I. &lt;a href=&#34;http://unfinished.bz/80&#34;&gt;This week‚Äôs episode&lt;/a&gt; is all about business insurance for freelancers and small businesses. We talked about public liability, professional indemnity, business contents and copyright infringement. It was great because I got to ask Ashley loads of questions I forgot to ask when she was helping me get insured!&lt;/p&gt;
