      src=&#39;Screen-Shot-2014-06-14-at-13.40.04.png&#39; alt=&#39;Visual - make it easy to read. Visuel - Facilitez la lecture&#39;
    /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It was tricky to fit the translated text into the slide designs. Usually I have as little text as possible on a slide, and French can be a lot longer than the English equivalent, so it took a while to ensure the slides were all readable on a projected screen.&lt;/p&gt;



