&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Sadly, &lt;a href=&#34;http://interlinkconference.com&#34;&gt;Interlink conference has been cancelled&lt;/a&gt;. I‚Äôm gutted that I won‚Äôt be visiting Canada this year, but I totally understand how difficult it is to run a conference, especially if you‚Äôre trying to put on the best possible event for your attendees and speakers.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
I‚Äôm running my [‚ÄòDesign theory for the web‚Äô workshop at Interlink conference](http://interlinkconference.com/workshops/#design-theory-web) in Canada on the 18th of June.


