&lt;p&gt;This week the¬†&lt;a href=&#34;http://alistapart.com/column/good-designers-good-clients&#34;&gt;first post was published on my A List Apart column&lt;/a&gt;. It‚Äôs a very exciting thing for me. I‚Äôve been reading A List Apart since I started learning about the web and loads of people I admire have written there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It‚Äôs good fun and a proper challenge having an editor working with me. I‚Äôve already learned a lot, and I hope to be slightly less hopeless at writing clearly as the months go by‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;


