&lt;p&gt;Andy Spicer also asked if I could share my &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bohemiancoding.com/sketch/&#34;&gt;Sketch&lt;/a&gt; mockups for the site design. &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.dropbox.com/s/13tfiy8xzworplz/Web%20talk%20dog%20walk%20mockup.zip&#34;&gt;You can download the zipped .sketch file here&lt;/a&gt;. I use &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.bohemiancoding.com/sketch/beta/&#34;&gt;the latest version of the Sketch beta&lt;/a&gt;, so you‚Äôll need to use this to open the file as it may not be compatible with older versions.&lt;/p&gt;
