&lt;p&gt;The last web talk dog walk was a success, with three of us (plus three dogs) taking in the slightly damp wilds of Sheepcote Valley. Now for the next one!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I was originally planning on making them fortnightly but have already failed as I wasn‚Äôt organised enough to sort one out this week. This means the next Web talk dog walk will be:&lt;/p&gt;
