&lt;p&gt;Last week I had a chat with the lovely Conor O‚ÄôDriscoll and last night he &lt;a href=&#34;http://theindustry.cc/2013/03/13/an-interview-with-laura-kalbag/&#34;&gt;published the interview on The Industry&lt;/a&gt;. We talking about design work, education and what I define as success, among other things.&lt;/p&gt;



    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;740&#39; height=&#39;165&#39;
      sizes=&#39;(min-width: 1380px) 750px, (min-width: 820px) 719px, (min-width: 740px) calc(-33.33vw &amp;#43; 875px), (min-width: 340px) calc(92.63vw - 39px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#39;
