	&lt;div class=&#34;comment-entry&#34;&gt;
		I find keeping up with the constant changes in the web dev world and the resources that go along with that the most exhausting thing (It does keep things interesting though!).  
&lt;p&gt;I‚Äôd be interested to know how people manage to fit ‚Äòeducation‚Äô into their busy schedules, as I often find my twitter favourites / instapaper / google reader lists spiral out of control‚Ä¶.
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
