	&lt;div class=&#34;comment-entry&#34;&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;The combination of staring at screens all day, sitting, trying to keep up with the industry, looking for work, doing work&amp;#8230; it all adds up to this mental juggling act and before we know it our brain and body fail.
&lt;p&gt;I‚Äôm working through similar issues. Being a one-person show as a freelancer is very difficult. Thanks for being honest. I wish you the best.&lt;/p&gt;	&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
