	&lt;div class=&#34;comment-entry&#34;&gt;
		I can completely relate to this ‚Äì; a bi-product of being a perfectionist, working hard towards my design career and having an almost full time admin job to hold down too. I find myself getting depressed and cabin fevery when I spend too long doing work in front of the computer so it definitely is worth considering our mental health, taking time away from the computer and doing things that refresh you. Wise words Laura!
