	&lt;div class=&#34;comment-entry&#34;&gt;
		Ah you all just need to man up! ;)
&lt;p&gt;I‚Äôve found cutting up the day and not worrying about constant work helps me too. Watch some TV while working, take a 10 minute nap, call someone, go see a film. Yes it does mean sometimes I have to work at night, but if I feel like I can then it helps me. It amazes me if you actually stop and look at an office how often people are actually not working. You just feel that if you work on your own or at home that you have to do more hours than anyone else.
