&lt;p&gt;After reading this brilliant &lt;a href=&#34;http://mac.appstorm.net/how-to/internet-howto/turning-mail-app-into-the-best-mac-email-app/&#34;&gt;Mac App Storm post on Turning Mail.app Into the Best Mac Email App&lt;/a&gt;, I was inspired to follow a lot of the tips to make my emails easier to handle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I made three Smart Mailboxes, following the tips I chose:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;‚ÄòFollow Up‚Äô which contains emails flagged with a green flag, using the shortcut of ‚åò‚áßg&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;‚ÄòNeeds Reply‚Äô which contains emails flagged with a blue flag, using the shortcut of ‚åò‚áßb&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;‚ÄòNeeds Attention‚Äô which contains emails flagged with a red flag, using the shortcut of ‚åò‚áßr&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The benefit of using the red flag for ‚ÄòNeeds Attention‚Äô as a way of noting emails which need organising into either of the other smart mailboxes is that Mail.app on the iPhone only supports the red flag. This means I can easily flag something for later with a red flag on my phone, and deal with it properly when I get to my laptop.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-problem&#34;&gt;The problem&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;However, I have a terrible memory for shortcut keys. I couldn‚Äôt remember which colours related to which mailboxes, and so couldn‚Äôt remember the relevant keyboard shortcuts (as these used the first letter of the name of the colour).&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;figure&gt;


    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;661&#39; height=&#39;376&#39;
      sizes=&#39;(min-width: 1380px) 750px, (min-width: 820px) 719px, (min-width: 740px) calc(-33.33vw &amp;#43; 875px), (min-width: 340px) calc(92.63vw - 39px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#39;
      srcset=&#39;https://laurakalbag.com/using-emoji-in-mail.app-to-make-better-visual-indicators/Screen-Shot-2013-02-10-at-15.10.31_huf7cc4fc9f24a9bab14a5b14f2f869873_44711_300x0_resize_mitchellnetravali_2.png 300w,/using-emoji-in-mail.app-to-make-better-visual-indicators/Screen-Shot-2013-02-10-at-15.10.31_huf7cc4fc9f24a9bab14a5b14f2f869873_44711_500x0_resize_mitchellnetravali_2.png 500w,/using-emoji-in-mail.app-to-make-better-visual-indicators/Screen-Shot-2013-02-10-at-15.10.31.png 661w&#39;
      src=&#39;Screen-Shot-2013-02-10-at-15.10.31.png&#39; alt=&#39;Mail.app smart mailboxes in the Favourites bar&#39;
