	&lt;div class=&#34;comment-entry&#34;&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Hi Laura,
&lt;p&gt;I must say, I‚Äôm at a loss for words, partially because (kind of like yourself) I never &lt;em&gt;really&lt;/em&gt; was exposed to any bad behaviour on conferences. But more importantly, and I cannot stress this enough, because I am stunned by the braveness you have to keep fighting despite the fact you‚Äôve never had any real setback during conferences. Don‚Äôt get this the wrong way though, I‚Äôm sure nobody wants to be called out as a token, I‚Äôm sure, but I‚Äôve seen people write crazy stuff on the internet as well, and yours seems still bareable compared to them. Yet, despite this, you still fight back, even if it was just to defend those whom are truely being bullied. Now that.. that‚Äôs a noble thing. It‚Äôs why I‚Äôm proud to know you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Keep fighting Laura, we‚Äôre behind you ;)&lt;/p&gt;
PS Hope I didn‚Äôt say/write anything offensive here? Sorry if I did.
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
