&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://laurakalbag.com/a-loveletter/&#34;&gt;Read the original post, ‚ÄòA loveletter‚Äô&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Following my &lt;a href=&#34;https://laurakalbag.com/learning-design/&#34; title=&#34;Learning Design&#34;&gt;learning design post&lt;/a&gt;, I‚Äôve started a little project called ‚Äúnew to design.‚Äù At the moment it just consists of &lt;a href=&#34;https://pinboard.in/u:laurakalbag/t:learn-design/&#34;&gt;a learn-design tag on my Pinboard bookmarks&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/newtodesign&#34;&gt;Twitter account @newtodesign &lt;/a&gt;so that I can share useful design resources (especially for those new to design.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the future, I hope it can be useful in other ways. Any suggestions or anything you want to see? &lt;a href=&#34;https://laurakalbag.com/contact-me/&#34; title=&#34;Contact Me&#34;&gt;You know how to get in touch‚Ä¶&lt;/a&gt;



