		&lt;p&gt;Hi Laura, Love what you‚Äôre doing here. I myself am a college student and I created [Student Guide Web Design](http://www.studentguidewebdesign.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow) simply out of frustration with the material I was being presented during my design education. I love helping others because it‚Äôs a great way for me to learn myself, but also helps others out who are also trying to overcome the same challenges (because I was there at one point!).
