	&lt;li class=&#34;comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1&#34; id=&#34;li-comment-424&#34;&gt;
			&lt;div class=&#34;comment-author vcard&#34;&gt;
			&lt;img alt=&#39;&#39; src=&#39;https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e165723531f696f9706fefc2ca78d287?s=72&amp;amp;d=mm&amp;amp;r=g&#39; srcset=&#39;https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e165723531f696f9706fefc2ca78d287?s=144&amp;amp;d=mm&amp;amp;r=g 2x&#39; class=&#39;avatar avatar-72 photo&#39; height=&#39;72&#39; width=&#39;72&#39; /&gt;&lt;cite class=&#34;fn&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#39;http://louisbullock.com.au&#39; rel=&#39;external nofollow&#39; class=&#39;url&#39;&gt;Louis Bullock&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/cite&gt;
				&lt;aside class=&#34;comment-meta commentmetadata&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#comment-424&#34;&gt;&lt;time datetime=&#34;2012-12-19T03:01:56+00:00&#34; pubdate class=&#34;published&#34;&gt;
		 at &lt;span class=&#34;hours&#34;&gt;03:01am&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/time&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/aside&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class=&#34;comment-entry&#34;&gt;
		Fantastic article, Laura, I‚Äôve now re-evaluated how I talk to others online, when to give critique and constructive criticism etc.
&lt;p&gt;I don‚Äôt know about you, but one my favourite things in this community is when a dev or designer takes on something I‚Äôve suggested or improves after listening to my criticism, or even respects it and acknowledges it. It‚Äôs an absolute delight, and what makes this community a wonderful place; I hope that it will continue to be a place of positivity, and supportiveness.
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li class=&#34;comment even thread-even depth-1&#34; id=&#34;li-comment-425&#34;&gt;
			&lt;div class=&#34;comment-author vcard&#34;&gt;
			&lt;img alt=&#39;&#39; src=&#39;https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2b4421b2aa8931592c57b61ca3b39d45?s=72&amp;amp;d=mm&amp;amp;r=g&#39; srcset=&#39;https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2b4421b2aa8931592c57b61ca3b39d45?s=144&amp;amp;d=mm&amp;amp;r=g 2x&#39; class=&#39;avatar avatar-72 photo&#39; height=&#39;72&#39; width=&#39;72&#39; /&gt;&lt;cite class=&#34;fn&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#39;http://next-nexus.info/&#39; rel=&#39;external nofollow&#39; class=&#39;url&#39;&gt;Michael.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/cite&gt;
				&lt;aside class=&#34;comment-meta commentmetadata&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#comment-425&#34;&gt;&lt;time datetime=&#34;2012-12-21T13:30:42+00:00&#34; pubdate class=&#34;published&#34;&gt;
