&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mail.app.&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;em&gt;Mac OSX default&lt;/em&gt;)¬†I want my email available offline and on my iPhone. Mail does that. It may not be feature-filled, but at least Google isn‚Äôt snooping around in there‚Ä¶&lt;/li&gt;
