		Very nice Laura, certainly gets across a lot of your personality starting with the typeface and then on to the illustrations and colours! It‚Äôs great, and everything you‚Äôve written is so honest and upfront.
&lt;p&gt;If I were to make comment it would be I‚Äôm never keen on underlined links (if you need to underline, use &lt;code&gt;border-bottom&lt;/code&gt; so you don‚Äôt interfere with descenders).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also, your (amazing) work doesn‚Äôt seem to take centre stage! Perhaps that‚Äôs what you wanted, but it‚Äôs like the 5th link on your navigation? I‚Äôd bring it to the fore and make your screenshots larger, and maybe cross-sell between sections a bit.&lt;/p&gt;
