&lt;p&gt;You‚Äôre very kind about my work, and I really appreciate the constructive criticism. I did think hard about how I wanted to represent myself, and really my primary goal for the site was to be as useful as possible for potential clients. Of course I want to be judged on my previous work, but I think it‚Äôs important that I provide other information about the kind of designer I am and what I‚Äôm like to work with.
