&lt;p&gt;This is my favourite part. There is no better way to motivate yourself than seeing how much exercise you‚Äôve been doing in statistic form. And if you‚Äôre competitive? You can also share your information with friends (this allows you to lock down or make public as much or as little info as you‚Äôd like) to compete and motivate yourself to beat the other people in your group with daily, weekly or lifetime scores.&lt;/p&gt;

