&lt;h3 id=&#34;food-log&#34;&gt;Food Log&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I truly believe that the best way to lose weight is to keep a food and drink diary. It really makes you realise what you‚Äôre putting into your body. The Fitbit food log helps with this as you can quickly enter in your foods from its extensive database, in whatever quantities suit you best. Like other food databases, it tends to mostly feature food from the US, but you can easily add new foods yourself, and they‚Äôve got a much better database of raw ingredients (fruit, veg etc.) than any other web app I‚Äôve used.&lt;/p&gt;

