&lt;h3 id=&#34;other-logs&#34;&gt;Other logs&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There‚Äôs also a whole host of other logs that you can use to keep an eye on your body. In case you couldn‚Äôt tell by now, I‚Äôm loving these stats. Nothing makes me feel quite so much like a future person than looking at graphs about my own body. I feel like an android (the cool robot, not the rubbish phone.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I make use of the Mood log a fair bit. I think it‚Äôs healthy to assess your mood from time to time, understand yourself better and try to get to the root of what‚Äôs making you feel happy or sad.&lt;/p&gt;

