&lt;h3 id=&#34;email-motivations&#34;&gt;Email Motivations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A lovely little addition to the Fitbit web app is the weekly stats you get sent via email. A nice little reminder of how you‚Äôre doing compared to last week, and a kick up the bum if you‚Äôve been lazy.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;figure&gt;


