		I‚Äôve been thinking about this since Mark‚Äôs talk too. I‚Äôd be up for a meetup group to critique work, although I don‚Äôt do much design at the moment, but I do work as a usability consultant so I guess I critique people‚Äôs work everyday! I‚Äôve been having occasional thoughts about an online critiquing platform for a while since somebody on an e-campaigning list I subscribe to mentioned it but with the focus on critiquing digital campaigns. I started scribbling down more ideas on this during Mark‚Äôs talk. What do you think of a website where people could submit designs and ask for honest feedback? I‚Äôve seen people do it on other forums, but nothing specific. Would you use such a site? (and maybe be interested in a little collaboration project on it :) )
