&lt;p&gt;For those who wanted my notes in an undigested, scatterbrained form, here‚Äôs images from my notebook. (&lt;a href=&#34;https://laurakalbag.com/digest-from-ampersand-conf/&#34;&gt;My digest is available too&lt;/a&gt;.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I‚Äôm a mind-mapping fiend, so I try to link with arrows where I can. Where new points were begun I just moved to another space on the page, so forgive the random appearance! There‚Äôs not much point apologising for my bad handwriting, I can‚Äôt &lt;em&gt;really&lt;/em&gt; help that (all caps is a pretty dodgy habit) but there are some points, notably during Jonathan Hoefler‚Äôs talk, where the lights were low so it‚Äôs particularly illegible there‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;
