&lt;p&gt;The squares aren‚Äôt all the way up to the edges, like the Moleskine, it has margins at the top and bottom of each page and a space for the date. It has contents pages for you to fill in and comes with labels so you can index your notebooks. It isn‚Äôt quite as big as a XLarge Moleskine, but is a more manageable size than the larger¬†Leuchtturm1917 notebooks and, being hardback, it makes it easier to handle.&lt;/p&gt;

