&lt;p&gt;Golding: There is a myth that being first is really important. You want to be the first to win not the first to market &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/bigmconf/status/49872937783799808&#34;&gt;From @bigmconf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
