&lt;p&gt;Golding: Study what else has succeeded, what has failed, and what you can take and project out in order to innovate &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/bigmconf/status/49873438013267968&#34;&gt;From @bigmconf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
