&lt;h3 id=&#34;lowercase-camelcase-or-other&#34;&gt;lowercase, CamelCase or Other?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The original name for Stockyoo was ‚ÄòStockYoo‚Äô with the uppercase S and Y. When I did my first draft of the logo design, I just went straight for all lowercase as I found it easier on the eye. Andy (quite rightly!) pointed out that it needed some uppercase for consistency when showing the name without the logo, but said he‚Äôd be ok with just the uppercase S, so we put it to the vote on Dribbble and Forrst and got 100% preference for the lowercase ‚Äòy‚Äô.&lt;/p&gt;

