		Dan,
&lt;p&gt;I canÔøΩt speak for your friendÔøΩs clients ‚Äì; but all my clients know the truth about our operation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;YouÔøΩd be surprised.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We (and it is a we in my case) do work for clients like Waitrose, John Lewis and WWE.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All of them know:&lt;/p&gt;
