&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If they call me at 5.35 I havenÔøΩt left the office&lt;/p&gt;
Also, people that work for large companies are people ‚Äì; first and foremost.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They get why youÔøΩd want to work from home.  Some of them are even jealous!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;God, IÔøΩd love not to have to commute for an hour each morning.  How wonderful. Lucky you!&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I had one client who used to work in the City and gave that up once she saw I was doing fine working from (what was then) a house with a sea view in Cornwall.&lt;/p&gt;
