Typekit brings those to-die-for fonts from top quality foundries to the web with a teensy bit of javascript. Typekit showcases [some of the most stunning fonts](http://typekit.com/foundries/veer) I‚Äôve ever seen and allows you to use them on your site in a way that is quick and easy, but still preserves the licensing and distribution control that the foundries and font designers need to keep them going.


  &lt;figure&gt;


    &lt;img
      class=&#39;landscape&#39;
      width=&#39;787&#39; height=&#39;376&#39;
