&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&#34;asterisk&#34;&gt;* I keep the ad-supported version of &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.atebits.com/tweetie-iphone/&#34;&gt;Tweetie&lt;/a&gt; for this reason, the ads are usually for top-quality, useful products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
